Notable people
* William J. Duffy – (1916–2013), American jurist and legislator. Duffy served in the Wisconsin State Assembly 1949–1950, and was elected a Wisconsin Circuit Court judge for Brown County, Wisconsin serving until his retirement in 1992. Born in North Branch.
* Stephanie Cholensky – Socialist Party USA Chair 
* Doug Mahnke – comic book writer

